Baaritaanka SARS-CoV-2 RNA ee loo adeegsaday fal-celinta silsiladda polymerase-ka ee ka-noqoshada (RT-PCR) ayaa loo isticmaalay sida shuruudaha ugu muhiimsan ee lagu ogaanayo COVID-19.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, sababtoo ah tirada badan ee natiijooyinka been abuurka ah, oo laga yaabo inay sii dardar geliyaan faafitaanka, calaamadaha bukaan-socodka ayaa bilaabay in loo isticmaalo baaritaanka (oo aan mar dambe ku saleysneyn kaliya RT-PCR) Shiinaha 13 Febraayo 2020.
