Sida borotiinka xubin ka ah, ACE2 ayaa ah meesha ugu weyn ee ay unugyada galaan qaar ka mid ah coronavirus-yada, oo ay ku jiraan HCoV-NL63, SARS-CoV (viruska keena SARS), iyo SARS-CoV-2 (viruska keena COVID-19).
