Isticmaalka ACE-yada ayaa sidoo kale la xiriiray hoos u dhaca dhimashada sambabaha, inkastoo natiijooyinku ay ka yaryihiin kuwa guud ahaan halista sambabaha.
Xanuunka sambabka ee aadanaha ee loo yaqaan recombinant human angiotensin 2 converting enzyme (rhACE2) waxaa loo soo jeedinayaa in lagu daweeyo xanuunka sanbabada ee daran waxaana la filayaa in uu hagaajiyo haemodynamics-ka sambabada iyo oksijiinta ku jirta doofaarka leh xanuunka sanbabada ee loo yaqaan ' lipopolysaccharide-induced acute respiratory distress syndrome'.
Waqtiga nuska ah ee uu ku noolaan karo rhACE2 aadanaha waa qiyaastii 10 saacadood, waqtiga uu wax ku qabana waa 30 daqiiqo marka lagu daro waqtiga uu wax ku qabanaayo waa 24 saac.
