Waxaa jira caddeyn muujineysa in hydroxychloroquine ay leedahay awood ka hortagga xasaasiyadda cytokine. Tocilizumab waxaa tilmaamaha daaweynta ku daray guddiga caafimaadka qaranka ee Shiinaha kadib markii daraasad yar la sameeyay.
Waxaa hadda lagu wadaa in dalka Talyaaniga lagu sameeyo tijaabo heer 2 ah oo aan kala sooc lahayn, kadib markii natiijooyin wanaagsan laga helay dadka qaba cudurka halista ah.
Baaritaankaas oo ay weheliso baaritaanka dhiigga ee loo yaqaano ' serum ferritin' si loo ogaado shoogga cytokine, waxaa looga baahan yahay in lagu baaro isbeddelka noocan ah, kaas oo loo malaynayo inuu sabab u yahay dhimashada dadka qaarkood.
Cudurka ka hortagga interleukin-6 waxaa FDA ogolaatay iyada oo ku saleysan daraasado kiis oo dib loo eegay oo loogu talagalay daaweynta steroid-ka oo loo yaqaan 'cytokine-refractory relapse syndrome' oo ay keento sabab kale, daaweynta CAR T cells, 2017.
Illaa iyo hadda ma jirto caddayn la baaray oo muujinaysa in tocilizumab uu yahay daawo waxtar leh oo lagu daweeyo CRS.
Kala bedelka unugyada difaaca jirka ee la xoojiyay oo la sifeeyay ee ay soo saaraan nidaamyada difaaca jirka ee dadka ka bogsaday COVID-19 si ay u siiyaan dadka u baahan ayaa loo baaray sidii hab aan tallaal ahayn oo ah tallaalka aan tallaalka ahayn.
Istaraatiijiyadkan waxaa loo tijaabiyay SARS wax natiijo ahna lama gaarin.
Ka-hortagga fayraska waa habka la filayo ee daaweynta lidka jirka ee la isticmaalo ay ka hortag u keento SARS-CoV-2.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, habab kale sida antibody-dependent cytotoxicity iyo/ ama phagocytosis ayaa suurtagal noqon kara.
Qaabab kale oo daaweyn antibiyootiko ah oo aan la isticmaalin, sida isticmaalka unugyada difaaca jirka ee loo yaqaan 'monoclonal antibodies', ayaa la soo saaray.
Wax soo saarka shaandhada dadka soo bogsashada ah, oo ah qaybta dareeraha ah ee dhiiga bukaanka bogsaday oo ay ku jiraan unugyada ka hortaga fayraska, ayaa la kordhin karaa si dhaqso loogu soo saaro.
